We are excited to welcome HELLA CHLUY 🇰🇭🇺🇸 to Sabaidee Fest as an influencer! 🎉 

Hella Chluy is a Cambodian-American comedian and musician known for his parodies and humorous songs that often focus on Cambodian-American culture. A Khmer Weird Al, if you will. 

He gained popularity through social media and video sharing platforms like YouTube. His work typically includes comedic skits and songs that reflect on the experiences and challenges faced by the Cambodian diaspora. 

His channel has evolved into travel vlogs and food content, however he is actively posting short form comedy on Tik Tok, Instagram, and Facebook. Hella Chluy hopes to inspire the next generation of Khmer artists and content creators for generations to come.

Come see him and your favorites at Sabaidee Fest 2024!🎊
